column2: SELECT FLOOR(sppParams.l) l,     AVG(s.z*#e5/cos(radians(sppParams.b))) v_doppler,     STDEV(s.z*#e5/cos(radians(sppParams.b)))/SQRT(COUNT(*)) error FROM  SpecObj s INNER JOIN sppParams ON s.specobjID = sppParams.specObjID WHERE s.z<# and s.z># and sppParams.feha># and sppParams.feha<# and sppParams.b<# GROUP BY FLOOR(sppParams.l) ORDER BY #
